{"name": "GC	NESIS the album cover 1/50", "description": "This is my first time ever publishing in Web3. 
I released an album in 2020 (GC)nesis) that I will be soon publishing it here too. 
The album talks about changes and every version of you that exists within them, so every song has a character that we created and did a photoshoot for each one to narrate the story. They all come together in the cover. It is so important to know every version of yourself to put them together to make you grow. Positive, empowering and honest. WE ARE ALL ONE. 
"GC)nesis" was my first ever album, the renaissance of Sofia Coll.  
I have been working on new dope music for these past years, traveling and creating a team. That's why I wanted to share here some of my work before moving into something new! The exclusive photoshoot of each character is coming soon! 
Now I am looking for founding and support for my new upcoming project!!! #excited <3 

But before.... this is GC	NESIS the album cover collection!!!!
